snippet.title: PS1 - Submarine Commander - LongPlay [4K]🔴
snippet.description:
PS1 - Submarine Commander - LongPlay [4K]🔴

I don't think a lot of people played this game, but i think this game should have had a bit more love, i want say it is a good game but i will say it is an interesting game with interesting story.

I really don't remember how i got this game, but i remember i used to play it and enjoyed it. There are a lot of tactics you can and should use to beat this game, or you just can cheat like i do :D
